Titolo: Crush, Crumble and Chomp!

Anno: 1981

Descrizione: Crush, Crumble and Chomp! is a 1981 video game where the player takes control of a movie monster and attacks a major city, such as New York or San Francisco. It was published in 1981 for the TRS-80, Apple II, and Atari 8-bit family. Ports to the VIC-20, Commodore 64, and MS-DOS were released later. Some versions were published under the company's original name of Automated Simulations, while the rest use Epyx.